      * Drug class: Diuretics;

        * Episodic Use (as needed): Yes; Chronic Use: Yes(b);
        * Restrictions: Non-narcotic analgesics only
      * Drug class: H2-Blockers/ PPI;

        * Episodic Use (as needed): Yes; Chronic Use: Yes(b);
